						               													<description>Love Hotel is a party game with teenagers, mainly girls, being the target audience. In the game Love Hotel you choose a (fictive) partner. Your goal is to get to the love suite before any of the other couples for some private time. You are only allowed to enter the love suite after you've collected four types of cushions for your bed. Let the race begin!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You and your opponents move around the board, answering questions and acting out tasks for each of the four categories. Doing so correctly will earn you a cushion of the corresponding color. Helping your opponent with a task will earn you a heart. Hearts can be used to buy cushions or to mend broken hearts. If you land on a broken heart tile and don't mend it (by choice or because you don't have any heart tokens) you risk losing one of your cushions. The first person to collect all four cushions and make it to the love suite wins the game!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
